cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.PL, cs.CE, cs.SE 

This paper discusses the implementation of a web-based database interface using Prolog, which is a programming language commonly used in the fields of artificial intelligence and logic programming (cs.AI, cs.PL). The interface is designed to provide access to integrated biochemical data, which falls under the category of databases (cs.DB). The paper also mentions the use of libraries and features that are relevant to computer engineering (cs.CE) and software engineering (cs.SE).
